reviewText: In this video, Mike Dooley talks about how he got his "second start" after his t-shirt business failed. He talks about the "baby steps" someone has to take to make their manifestations come true. I highly recommend it. I got more out of his story then most other law of attraction videos.
A lot of good energy and encouragement.  Dooley's fans will enjoy this.  If you are a Dooley fan, you will enjoy this.
